{"word":"ἁρπαλέος","slug":"ἁρπαλέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁρπαλέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρπάζω'><el>ἁρπάζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>greedy</i>: <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>ἁρπαλέως</el>, <i>greedily, eagerly</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>attractive, alluring</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}